                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>My dear <addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I enclose a few notes for the next<lb/> number of your <add>?</add>\n                journal I hope I have not made<lb/> them too long. You are aware <persName>Mr De\n                    Sola</persName> established<lb/> a Sunday school &amp; altho 3 mos in\n                    <add>?</add> I<lb/> can assure you we were all <add>?</add> at the progress<lb/>\n                displayed by all the children. The school numbers<lb/> about 20 children which is a\n                good many for our small<lb/> community. I have another piece of good news<lb/> to\n                communicate which is that one of our people<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Samuel Benjamin</persName> has been elected <add>?</add> city<lb/>\n                councillor, for one of our principal handsâ€”he<lb/> is the first Jew who has\n                    <add>?</add> been so honored<lb/> in <placeName>Canada</placeName> and from his\n                sterling integrity &amp; sound<lb/> judgement I am convinced he will do great\n                credit<lb/> to himself &amp; his people</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3td9nr2p/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
